517
00:23:15,215 --> 00:23:15,782
-What?

518
00:23:15,882 --> 00:23:18,148
Big sister Shampoo?

519
00:23:18,248 --> 00:23:22,015
You're from the same
Chinese Amazon tribe as her?

520
00:23:22,115 --> 00:23:24,715
Next time on Ranma 1/2,
"Two Too-Violent Girls,

521
00:23:24,815 --> 00:23:26,148
Ling-Ling and Lung-Lung."

